{"tid":495884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【冇電都用到】八達通進化！夥三星推Mobile Pay 嘟手機就搭到車","createTime":"2017-12-11T07:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T08:20:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfc41934102976d39fa8e9a0bc9ff7ef6127d7d","tid":495884,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/large/1512975582_baa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Flarge%2F1512975582_baa3.jpg&h=1655215d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八達通公佈，伙拍Samsung推出「Smart Octopus」。只要將八達通加入Samsung Pay系統，就可以拎部電話當八達通用，除搭車外，可以用於停車場、出入門禁、零售商店等，更可以翻查最多40個交易紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n根據介紹，即使手機關機亦可以用，就算無電都可以用。增值方面，照舊可現金或自動增值，更用用samsung pay 信用卡增值，額度為300至1000元，惟八達通公司會收取2.5% 手續費。八達通指，Samsung Pay 的Smart Octopus 與一般八達通卡無異，12月14日，即星期四可以開始使用。<br />\n<br />\n如果用現有八達通卡轉移到手機，卡內的日日賞、乘車優惠、門禁、餘額等均可轉移至手機，但轉移後原有的八達通卡就不能再用。不希望失去舊卡，可以在內開一張就的智能八達通。<br />\n<br />\n首屆段只適用於成人及長者八達通，手機方面現支援Samsung Note8 、S8、S8+。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171211/57567328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57567328&d=K3Mti2WBIh1zTkKWbeZO7AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8343b75a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57567328&h=19f9bb44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171211/57567328</a>"},{"pid":"58a13ae9f16141a85f34a8f4a6749221186b16b6","tid":495884,"uid":144063,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"e86b469d8f2268d410faaf6bc50704795b42a12a","tid":495884,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"不希望失去舊卡，可以在內開一張就的智能八達通。<br />\n<br />\n幾好咁喎 不過佢UP乜春"},{"pid":"7e7e237bacfe1f3323a1bbf301d07b5f70bcbb13","tid":495884,"uid":38540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:15:47.000Z","msg":"android 狗也不屌"},{"pid":"a0e90b87f3a6e7223bef461ba4d6610bc535d196","tid":495884,"uid":37136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:17:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但轉移後原有的八達通卡就不能再用</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c6b7a71fd0578221cfce7835ccd8d3e7601f53","tid":495884,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">但轉移後原有的八達通卡就不能再用</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜即係日本suica 入apple pay 咁"},{"pid":"72de9dd12693523e2fb2caf83481c08744674808","tid":495884,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"我十年前已經識釘張50蚊係100蚊紙上面啦"},{"pid":"a8ab2e20da2f2623d713444ea94ac6cb53b54ab7","tid":495884,"uid":60536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢係咪有語癌"},{"pid":"19266b4b4ecc9f901d6a255c37d456d33ff9a7df","tid":495884,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢係咪有語癌</blockquote><br />\n應該係語音輸入又唔翻Check"},{"pid":"180161c898afe21ad3520b173598143f33b10f28","tid":495884,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不希望失去舊卡，可以在內開一張就的智能八達通。<br />\n<br />\n幾好咁喎 不過佢UP乜春</blockquote><br />\n我估佢打錯字姐<br />\n如果冇理解錯咪即係開張新卡<br />\n因為一入咗電話 張實體卡就廢咗<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;實體八達通經轉移後會被取消而不可再用。並只適用於印有9個數字號碼（即8個數字加括號內的1個數字）&rdquo;"},{"pid":"8fc23a2e62c99e355ab91c1e6628e7565e9689ca","tid":495884,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ed8873002998135547bbc5e0837c4ac233aa80c","tid":495884,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"root 機都唔用得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e332a19e88d1425b289ef4a8b2975a5ea48e953d","tid":495884,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:57:13.000Z","msg":"八達通公司會收取2.5% 手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094d5389ff9602531de1ba62cfb9dfa1338f2d53","tid":495884,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八達通公司會收取2.5% 手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔洗擔心 小童未有得用<br />\n乖 去做下閱讀理解先"},{"pid":"144a2631ffe4f534a8116251ce448b5f1d292bb7","tid":495884,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八達通公司會收取2.5% 手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只限用3叔pay增值only<br />\n可去7仔,mtr個d no charge"},{"pid":"3b3f89c6d31222c11b6e5c0c2f73d0592a3d8c7f","tid":495884,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:03:01.000Z","msg":"無電都用到仲有咩保安可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c0a6383e751cc3d48790849c4a675e179bfd71","tid":495884,"uid":159631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"e0cb4166129f4d6afbece7424700d39b70aceb87","tid":495884,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無電都用到仲有咩保安可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<br />\n好似本身張八達通咁日日都要叉電就最好"},{"pid":"4b575b9ce5df49318a14801d286bb614c9ac24c7","tid":495884,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無電都用到仲有咩保安可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<br />\n好似本身張八達通咁日日都要叉電就最好</blockquote><br />\napple android pay 電話有電用<br />\n電話無電實體信用卡亦用得<br />\n<br />\n八達通完全同用家脫節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9063e3487115204742159631f561db5b218c0f0","tid":495884,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"轉用apple pay android pay就係因為有tokenization<br />\n<br />\n加密無人知卡號 保安得到提升<br />\n<br />\n依家八達通完全為做而做<br />\n<br />\n熄左機都得<br />\n<br />\n我洗鬼入落去電話咩"},{"pid":"528ca88be550b86d0061743a71aafd5b30af6dee","tid":495884,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"成個project 都低能, 部電話拎去整, 張卡作又廢, 即係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}